              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Current Board</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6">
              <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-2">
                <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-red-600">7-0</span>
                <span class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Disadvantage</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Parents who prioritize academic excellence and transparency are currently underrepresented on the Orange Unified School Board.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-xl p-4">
              <p class="text-sm text-red-800 font-medium">
                <strong>What this means:</strong> Critical decisions about curriculum, spending, and policies are being made without adequate parent representation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Take Action Card -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl text-white">
